            <title>[LU-13539] Some LASSERTF are missing terminating newlines</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13539</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Messages like to following are helpful for developers but confusing to admins.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;2020-05-08T08:53:19.366356-05:00 c0-0c2s2n0 format at import.c:1501:ptlrpc_import_recovery_state_machine doesn&apos;t end in newline
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are a few LASSERTF cases that do not have terminating newlines ... lets just fix those few stragglers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
